{"tid":653932,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵返套漫畫叫咩名","createTime":"2018-05-05T07:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T15:09:23.000Z","uid":44090,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"37cc6ea065a79003950618ec9cc1b49ed34853ee","tid":653932,"uid":44090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:33:44.000Z","msg":"套野係單元式好多故事既<br />\n<br />\n其中一個係講有隻手鐲可以帶比人好運<br />\n但係會係令其他人有厄運<br />\n最係飛機臨失事既時候女主角帶左隻手鐲落飛機個手柄度，全機無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一個係講有個男人得到個會講野既人頭<br />\n幫佢賭錢贏好多<br />\n最後賭3鋪輪盤<br />\n第三鋪係呃個男人既<br />\n但係比男人識穿左<br />\n因為佢爸爸既遺書提左佢第三下係fake<br />\n最後沖左個人頭落廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人記得本野叫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1ba746c57b97fd76edf07b60d8b9c007f2e6b9","tid":653932,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:35:27.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cbd2fad2e61fe3cf7181aa418033ae01c4c392d","tid":653932,"uid":14606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T07:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/154442_c5c96cee0c69ebb6cee28bcce4204148.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F154442_c5c96cee0c69ebb6cee28bcce4204148.JPG&h=90a961fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/154428_52ac3e026450c2c6de30cacd9276219c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F154428_52ac3e026450c2c6de30cacd9276219c.JPG&h=9281eafb&s={SIZE}\"